00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:09.679
hi I'm Peg from Sony

00:00:09.679 --> 00:00:14.019
did you know that if your cell phone has
the Android 2.1 operating

00:00:14.019 --> 00:00:21.119
system or higher it can be used as a
remote control for your Sony internet tv with Google tv

00:00:21.119 --> 00:00:24.969
were going to show you how to set up
your phone to use it as a remote control

00:00:24.969 --> 00:00:29.160
for your Sony internet tv with Google tv

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:33.620
it is important to note that the Sony
internet tv must first be connected to a

00:00:33.620 --> 00:00:36.300
wireless home network

00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:40.920
the phone will use your wireless network
as a method of communication to the 

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:44.030
Sony internet tv with Google tv

00:00:44.030 --> 00:00:49.160
you will need to download and install the
Google tv remote application

00:00:49.160 --> 00:00:52.820
it is a free download from the Android Market

00:00:52.820 --> 00:00:56.400
please read the terms before installing

00:00:56.400 --> 00:00:58.020
let's get started

00:00:58.020 --> 00:01:01.220
press and hold the Fn button

00:01:01.220 --> 00:01:06.090
and then press the number one button on
the keypad remote control to bring up

00:01:06.090 --> 00:01:08.300
the Settings menu

00:01:08.300 --> 00:01:14.460
scroll and select Input device

00:01:14.460 --> 00:01:17.890
press Enter

00:01:17.890 --> 00:01:24.660
when the Input device screen displays
select Mange IP remotes

00:01:24.660 --> 00:01:28.869
now select the Connect to new IP Remotes option

00:01:28.869 --> 00:01:33.060
and place a green check mark in the box

00:01:33.060 --> 00:01:37.720
when finished press the Home button

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:42.930
open the Google tv remote application on
your phone

00:01:42.930 --> 00:01:48.710
when the Google tv remote app detects the
Sony internet tv with Google tv

00:01:48.710 --> 00:01:52.560
select Connect

00:01:52.560 --> 00:01:56.170
Pair IP remote appears on the tv screen

00:01:56.170 --> 00:02:00.600
and displays a PIN code to be used with
the phone

00:02:00.600 --> 00:02:11.589
enter the PIN code displayed on the tv
screen into the Enter PIN code window on your phone

00:02:11.589 --> 00:02:13.879
and then select Pair

00:02:13.879 --> 00:02:18.239
a brief message will display on the
Sony internet tv screen

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:21.199
to indicate that the pairing is complete

00:02:21.199 --> 00:02:28.319
you are now able to control your tv
using the remote application on your phone

